    "Larger models demonstrate lower Intentionality, but higher Self-Efficacy.",
    "Llama2 variants with more parameters have lower Intentionality, but higher Self-Efficacy.",
    "This suggests that while a larger model size can enhance the expression of preferences, it might not necessarily facilitate the sustained pursuit of those preferences and reasons over multiple conversational turns.",
